{"tid":2347210,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"反省文！不是知道“Izone”的人就叫“wizone ”","createTime":"2020-12-31T01:05:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T07:38:17.000Z","uid":88491,"like":11,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6bad70ccc92d32b9c702cd062137f41ec431c23a","tid":2347210,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T01:05:41.000Z","msg":"不是知道&ldquo;Izone&rdquo;的人就叫&ldquo;wizone &rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n不是存了多少張Izone照片的人就叫&ldquo;wizone &rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n不是只要喜歡Izone臉孔的就叫&ldquo;wizone &rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n不是天天嚷嚷卻不動手做一件對Izone有利的事的人就叫&ldquo;wizone&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n我曾經看過一個文章裡一位親說：喜歡Izone的可以叫Izone飯，但Izone飯不等於wizone 。摸著心臟，好好問問自己，真的愛他們到某種地步了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWizone這個名字，是值得驕傲一生的名字<br />\n<br />\n這裡面包含了多少的淚水、艱辛、忍耐。<br />\n<br />\n但是因為那群少女，這個名字就算是在淚水裡面也在閃閃發光<br />\n<br />\nWizone，不是所有人都叫wizone<br />\n<br />\nWizone指你愛著那十二個少女，同樣的愛著一個不少，並且在心裡清清楚楚的知道，Izone，少了一個也不叫Izone<br />\n<br />\nIzone們走過來的多少不容易，除了我們還有誰知道？<br />\n<br />\n她們憑著那一份對舞台的執念走到了現在<br />\n<br />\n為了誰？<br />\n<br />\n只有Wizone。"},{"pid":"700f787ddf422c9efdcb52794a897b4968d96aea","tid":2347210,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T01:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"0bb9188daf38598647984374827de531a6a0e144","tid":2347210,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T01:06:42.000Z","msg":"好文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01a3e1e4794ee4997841af9582e51